<div type="definition">

    <p resp="#chris" modified="2021-03-19T14:24:20.424+09:00">YIELD one's HIGH OFFICE as RULER to ANOTHER, CONFORMING to one's OWN DECISION.X</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>Ra4ng 讓 refers to abdication with a focus on this act being in favour of a successor.</p>
<p>Sha4n 禪 refers to abdication with a focus on this act being one of selflessness or lack of mundane ambition.</p>
